”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
DMV Private School News is a skill to help families learn about private and independent schools in the Washington, DC metropolitan area. Our flash briefings will include open house information, podcasts, latest private school news, and more.

Please send us an email at info@dcschoolhub.com if you have suggestions for additional content.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
